     4.1.0

      Introduced $_COOKIE.
      Note that the deprecated $HTTP_COOKIE_VARS
      did exist previously.

  &reftitle.examples;



    $_COOKIE example


<?php
echo 'Hello ' . htmlspecialchars($_COOKIE["name"]) . '!';
?>



     Assuming the "name" cookie has been set earlier

